data.description: WOW! Your home has plenty of space and over $35,000 in upgrades. Your 4 bed, 3.5 bath home has it all and backs up to a beautiful green belt! You have an elevated great room with 11' high ceilings, 2.5 car garage, formal dining, quartz counter tops in the kitchen, cultured marble counter tops in the bathrooms, and your home is connected to a Smart Home feature and conveniently located close to Copper Sky Complex. Enjoy your newly landscaped turf and brand new 10x14 Gazebo! Come visit your beautiful new home today.
